{"tid":483922,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[HDD] 隻硬碟咁既聲有無問題?","createTime":"2017-11-29T15:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T02:42:54.000Z","uid":155737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2eb12b8eef9ffe1be70d28f1e7a813c80e047757","tid":483922,"uid":155737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:03:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>問題︰<br />\n火牛有輕微滋滋聲，<br />\n但係輕輕禁住隻牛出風位 塊格仔鐵網就無聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係唔關內膽事?</blockquote><br />\n自推，繼續問<br />\n- HDD 容量大&amp;高watt數係咪要預番隻風扇俾佢?<br />\n4TB idle 46度，連續寫入5MB/s 會keep住喺48/49左右<br />\n官方operational limit係55度...</blockquote><br />\n拆呢塊機箱內籠分隔板會唔會涼D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAAM無得調，APM調左最細</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://vocaroo.com/i/s0lSHNZgg4XM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvocaroo.com%2Fi%2Fs0lSHNZgg4XM&d=wkr3AHclfUVBQTTw8p030ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=a8ced353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vocaroo.com/i/s0lSHNZgg4XM</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">達達聲</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開始驚<br />\n求其搵左個網upload段錄音<br />\n型號係Toshiba MD04ACA400，好新淨<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tqIt3oQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtqIt3oQ.png&h=099856cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCrystalDiskInfo睇唔到有問題，<br />\n溫度idle 46度，運作再高D<br />\n<br />\n而家做緊disk scan......但如果衰bad heads既話係唔係唔好亂scan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n極度懷疑法記個日送貨炒車先咁多硬件問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c209199a49a1ddf98afef5b724fa3211cca5f2de","tid":483922,"uid":28580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:08:41.000Z","msg":"有D有聲係正常,無壞無B仔人地都唔會換比你"},{"pid":"953a967c0f35d1b8ca2a30e1ce66efc5f68a9eb5","tid":483922,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T01:39:56.000Z","msg":"天氣凍都51度，高高地<br />\n夏天時幾多度？"},{"pid":"1056322f286f7fdaaeed1402d129ba81965ed217","tid":483922,"uid":155737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T02:42:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天氣凍都51度，高高地<br />\n夏天時幾多度？</blockquote><br />\n無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都驚緊呢樣野"}]}